          <div class="bg-white border-2 border-slate-200 p-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3 uppercase">NEIGHBORHOOD KNOWLEDGE</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600">From century homes in Cabbagetown to new builds in Vaughan, we know each area's specific waterproofing challenges.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white border-2 border-slate-200 p-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3 uppercase">GTA WEATHER PATTERNS</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600">25 years of experience with Toronto's freeze-thaw cycles, spring melts, and summer downpours.</p>
